card.desc:
Firestore schema

‌

```
users/{uid} = {
  // ─── Core auth info ───
  email: string,
  displayName: string | null,     // nickname
  createdAt: Timestamp,
  hasCompletedOnboarding: boolean,

  // ─── Onboarding selections ───
  goal: string | null,            // "Build Muscle", etc.
  experience: string | null,      // "Beginner", etc.
  trainingDays: number | null,
  samplePlan: array | null,

  // ─── Profile sub-object ───
  profile: {
    gender: string | null,        // "Male", "Female", "Other"
    age: number | null,
    height: number | null,        // in cm
    weight: number | null,        // in kg
    units: "metric" | "imperial", // display units
  },

  // ─── Future expansions ───
  stats: {
    totalWorkouts: number,
    lastWorkout: Timestamp | null,
  }
}
```

